data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in Lithonia, Georgia! This recently renovated residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. As you step through the front door, you are greeted by an open living space with new flooring throughout. The living room is a cozy retreat with a fireplace and ample natural light streaming through the windows. The kitchen is a perfect setting for preparing delicious meals and entertaining guests featuring newer white kitchen cabinets and stainless steel appliances. The spacious primary bedroom offers a peaceful retreat for the homeowners. The en-suite private full bathroom features a large, granite countered vanity. The other two bedrooms are thoughtfully designed to provide comfort and privacy, perfect for a family or to provide extra living space. There is another full bathroom off the hall. A back porch invites you to sit back, relax, and enjoy the tranquility of the outdoors. Conveniently located to I-20 for quick travels to Atlanta, as well as being close to several local parks. This gorgeous home is a wonderful opportunity to experience comfortable living in a welcoming community. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer, a growing family, or someone looking to downsize, this residence offers a perfect blend of convenience and charm!
